<Defs>

  <ThingDef ParentName="AnimalThingBase">
    <defName>BOB_TyrannosaurusRex</defName>
    <label>tyrannosaurus rex</label>
    <devNote>tyrannosaurus rex</devNote>
    <description>A massive, ancient killer bred for dominance. Its bite crushes bone and its charge ruptures lines, leaving only devastation in its wake.\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;Gameplay effect:&lt;/color&gt; When angered, it will release a terror roar just like the alpha thrumbo, which scares away nearby hostile humans and animals. If you tame one, you can use this power as well.</description>
